ERD (Entity-Relationship Diagram):

Entities:
Energy_Sources (Source_ID, Source_Name, Type, Cost_Per_KWh)
Households (Household_ID, Location, Energy_Consumption, Income_Level)
Energy_Providers (Provider_ID, Provider_Name, Area_Covered)
Energy_Access (Access_ID, Household_ID, Provider_ID, Source_ID, Access_Date)
Relationships:
Households are provided energy by Energy_Providers.
Energy_Providers offer various Energy_Sources.
Households have records of energy access.
